title: At Home From Church
creator: Sarah Orne Jewett
description: LibriVox rvolunteers bring you 14 recordings of At Home From Church by Sarah Orne Jewett. This was the Fortnightly Poetry project for June 19, 2011. Jewett possessed a keen descriptive gift that William Dean Howells called "an uncommon feeling for talk — I hear your people." (Summary from Wikipedia) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (10MB)
subject: librivox; literature; poetry; audiobook; fiction; music; nature; religion
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
